    • invokeDrop

      public static void invokeDrop​(long countdown, org.schema.game.common.controller.SegmentController ship, org.schema.common.util.linAlg.Vector3i sector, boolean isJump, boolean force)
      will drop the given ship out of warp after x seconds to specified sector. will not check if ship is allowed to drop, only if it already has a drop queued. Automatically handles effects etc.
      Parameters:
      countdown - do jump in x second
      ship - ship to warp
      sector - targeted sector to drop into
      isJump - is a jump or an autodrop, will empty warpdrive if true
      force - overwrite all checks, admin
